export const supabaseGitHub = createClient(url, anon, {
  auth: {
    storageKey: 'sb-github-connect',
    persistSession: false,
    autoRefreshToken: false,
  },
});


persistSession: false can work, but it also makes popup session retrieval more fragile because it relies purely on in-memory parsing of the hash.

✅ Recommended change:

set persistSession: true (but keep the unique storageKey)

keep autoRefreshToken: false (fine)

This won’t override your main ThamOS session because the storage key is separate — it just makes the popup flow more reliable.

